query:
SELECT c.id, c.concertDate, a.name as artist, v.name as venue, v.city, v.latitude, v.longitude 
FROM concerts c 
JOIN artists a ON c.artistId = a.id 
JOIN venues v ON c.venueId = v.id 
WHERE c.id = 270001
